dct_title_s: Vorder-Asien nach dem Stand der topographischen Kenntnis für 1914 / dargestellt von Dr. Hans Fischer.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Ancillary continuation to the main map: Irak-Arabi (Süd Mesopotamien oder Babylonien). Includes map of Freist, Saxony, Scale 1:3,7000,00 as comparative area. In lower right margin:"Leitung: Prof. Paul Langhans." Original map  is filed in the Map/Geospatial Center. A map reproduction is attached to companion volume: Locate by call number: G1 .M588 66 Jahr., 1920.
